<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error 500</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/default/app.min.css">
    <style>
        .error-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
        }

        .error-content {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 150px;
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: white;
            color: #f5576c;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="error-page">
        <div class="error-content">
            <div class="error-code">500</div>
            <div class="error-message">Error del servidor</div>
            <p>Ha ocurrido un error interno. Por favor intenta m√°s tarde.</p>
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-home">Volver al inicio</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>